[normal]Barry Tootell[bold]: 
[normal]At
[normal] the end of 2011, 
[normal]beginning 
[normal]2012
[normal],
[normal] we were going through the consideration of our indicative offer to Lloyds
[normal]. W
[normal]e were very clear that we had to make this economically viable and we were doing a lot of analysis to make sure that it did do just that
[normal], and then
[normal],
[normal] d
